---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Mobile UI Development">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-paint-brush"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Engaging Mobile User Interface Design</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies incorporates advanced user interface patterns and designs to provide users an impressive, engaging and unforgettable mobile experience. Our professional team is actively involved at every step — decision-making, optimisation and flexible UI design — to deliver outstanding results.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-apple"></i></div>
            <h5>iPhone &amp; iPad UI</h5>
            <p>Custom mobile application user interface design for iPhone and iPad, crafted to match Apple's Human Interface Guidelines.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-puzzle-piece"></i></div>
            <h5>Widgets &amp; Gadgets</h5>
            <p>Mobile widget and gadget development — interactive mini-apps that add value and keep users engaged within your interface.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-th"></i></div>
            <h5>Mobile Themes</h5>
            <p>Custom mobile theme design that gives your application a consistent, branded look across all screen sizes and orientations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-picture-o"></i></div>
            <h5>Graphics &amp; Icons</h5>
            <p>Mobile-optimised graphics and icon design — crisp, purpose-built assets that look sharp on retina and high-DPI displays.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-hand-o-up"></i></div>
            <h5>Interactive Design</h5>
            <p>Immediate, responsive feedback to user actions — creating the kind of interactive experience that keeps users coming back.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-sliders"></i></div>
            <h5>UX Optimisation</h5>
            <p>A creative approach to user experience optimisation, ensuring the final UI design is both appealing and highly user-friendly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
